  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the project is to predict the patient under conservative therapy as a function of
      the patient Classification of Rommens and Hofmann and other potential prognostic factors. A
      corresponding prognostic score may be used in the future by patients and attending physicians
      support joint decision between surgical and conservative treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
